			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can't modify the translation of a 6-bit color number to an RGB value; that's controlled by a mask ROM within the PPU. But you can patch the ROMs to use different color numbers, such as using $26 or $36 for skin tones where the game uses the more orange $27 or $37, or using $00 and $10 for grays where the game uses $2D and $3D. And you could modify the ROMs not to use color emphasis. But that's about it.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

